# Design Language - Group Project

## Core Principles
- **Minimalism**: Clean, uncluttered interfaces with plenty of white space
- **Left Alignment**: All content should be left-aligned for better readability
- **Consistency**: Uniform spacing, typography, and visual elements across all components
- **Accessibility**: Ensure all elements are accessible and responsive

## Typography
- **Primary Font**: System fonts (-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif)
- **Headings**: Use semibold weight (font-weight: 600) for all headings
- **Body Text**: Regular weight (font-weight: 400) for body content
- **Line Height**: 1.6 for body text, 1.2 for headings
- **Font Sizes**:
  - H1: 48px (36px on mobile)
  - H2: 32px (28px on mobile)
  - H3: 24px (20px on mobile)
  - Body: 18px (16px on mobile)
  - Small: 14px



## Spacing & Layout
- **Padding Ratios**: Follow the ratio Left:1, Right:1, Top:0.5, Bottom:0.5
  - Example: If left/right padding is 20px, top/bottom should be 10px
- **Container**: Max-width 1200px, centered with auto margins
- **Sections**: 40px vertical padding (80px on desktop for hero sections)
- **Elements**: 10px base unit for consistent spacing

## Border Radius
- **Interactive Elements**: 6px border radius for modern, soft appearance
- **Apply to**: buttons, input fields, and clickable elements
- **Cards/Containers**: Minimize usage, prefer clean flat design for forms

## Components Standards

### Buttons
- **Primary Button**: Notion blue (#388fe5) background, white text, hover darker with lift effect
- **Secondary Button**: Transparent background, Notion blue border and text, hover with subtle background
- **Hover Effects**: Slight vertical lift (translateY(-1px)) with shadow
- Padding: 8px 16px (following design ratio)
- Border radius: 6px for modern rounded appearance
- Font weight: 500 (medium)
- Font size: 14px
- Transition: all 0.2s ease for snappy interactions

### Navigation
- **Background**: White in light mode (#ffffff), dark in dark mode (#191919)
- **Logo**: Full "Group Project" text, xl size, semibold weight
- **Links**: Slate-500 color, hover to primary text color
- **Theme Toggle**: Circular, filled button matching register button style
- Padding ratios maintained, smooth transitions

### Cards/Containers
- **Forms**: No background or borders - clean minimal styling
- **Other containers**: White background (#ffffff) with slate-200 borders (#e2e8f0) in light mode
- **Dark Mode**: Dark surface (#2f2f2f) with slate-600 borders (#475569)
- Border radius: 6px for interactive elements
- Consistent padding following the ratio system
- Avoid excessive card styling for forms

### Forms
- **Layout**: Left-aligned with max-width constraint (max-w-md = 448px)
- **Input fields**: 6px border radius, 8px padding vertical, 12px horizontal
- **Buttons**: 8px padding vertical, 16px horizontal with slight hover lift effect
- **Light**: Border slate-200, focus to primary blue with subtle shadow
- **Dark**: Border slate-600, focus to primary blue
- Smooth transitions (0.2s ease)
- No background cards for form containers

## Responsive Design
- **Mobile First**: Design for mobile, enhance for desktop
- **Breakpoints**: 768px for tablet/desktop changes
- **Navigation**: Stack vertically on mobile with 20px gap
- **Typography**: Reduce font sizes appropriately on mobile
- **Spacing**: Reduce padding/margins on smaller screens

## Interactive States
- **Hover**: Smooth transitions (0.3s ease)
- **Focus**: Clear visual indicators
- **Active**: Subtle feedback for user actions
- **Disabled**: Reduced opacity and no pointer events

## Code Standards
- Use CSS custom properties for consistent values
- Follow BEM methodology for class naming when applicable
- Ensure all interactive elements have proper accessibility attributes
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Maintain consistent indentation and formatting

